           "UHM T₃ — path-b baseline");
}

@test
fn test_uhm_in_l_cls_top_T4() {
    // FLAGSHIP: UHM T₄ — UHM ∈ L_Cls^top + MSFS L_Cls^top witness
    // corollary. Together with Diakrisis 106.T this gives TWO
    // independent witnesses that L_Cls^top is non-empty.
    assert(diakrisis_theorem_uhm_T4_in_l_cls_top(),
           "UHM T₄ — UHM ∈ L_Cls^top");
    assert(diakrisis_uhm_msfs_l_cls_top_witness(),
           "UHM → MSFS L_Cls^top witness corollary");
